以下是戰士的屬性分配參考(轉載自CASTERSREALM)<br>
Barbarian 133 105 87 75 70 60 55 <br>
Dark Elf 95 75 90 75 83 99 60 <br>
Dwarf 120 100 80 90 83 60 45 <br>
Gnome 95 80 90 85 67 98 60 <br>
Half Elf 105 80 95 85 60 75 75 <br>
Halfling 105 85 100 90 80 47 50 <br>
Human 110 85 80 75 75 75 75 <br>
Iksar 100 80 95 90 80 75 55 <br>
Ogre 140 132 85 85 67 60 37 <br>
Troll 128 119 93 85 60 52 40 <br>
Wood Elf 100 75 100 80 80 75 75<br>
(為分配過點數之後的數值)<br>
